    "Walter Brueggemann, Warren Carter": "On Hagar, Phyllis Trible, Texts of Terror, 9 - 3 5 . On Abraham `[char_Abraham_Exo_17]`'s shabby treat\u00ad\n[v_Gen_12_12] [v_Gen_12_13] ment of Sarah `[char_Sarah_Ref]`, Gen 12:12-13; 20:13; his xenophobia, Gen 12:10-20; 20:8-18.\n[v_Gen_16_6] Sarah `[char_Sarah_Ref]` claims to be wronged by Abraham `[char_Abraham_Exo_17]` (Gen 16:6), and Abimelech protests his\n[v_Gen_20_9] wrong actions (Gen 20:9).\n[v_Dan_2_37] [v_Dan_2_38] [v_Dan_2_39] [v_Dan_2_40] [v_Dan_2_41] [v_Dan_2_42] [v_Dan_2_43] [v_Dan_2_44] [v_Dan_2_45]"
